title: Spider-Man DESTROYS Star Wars on Wokeness

media:group.media:title: Spider-Man DESTROYS Star Wars on Wokeness
media:group.media:description:
Everyone liked Spider-Man Into The Spider Verse, yet many of the same fans hated Star Wars The Last Jedi. Both films about fan favorite icon heroes who have fallen from grace and lost their hero status. So how did Spider Man do it right, where Star Wars did it so wrong? Watch and find out! With Disney and Sony are having these financial disagreements and Spider-Man being kicked out of the MCU we may have to rely only on animated movies for quality Spider-Man!  PSA Sitch
